title: Canberra’s newest event for dog lovers to debut soonTravelandtourworld.com
text:
Canberra’s newest event for dog lovers to debut soon Published on : Tuesday, July 7, 2015
Canberra’s newest event for lovers of dogs is set to debut at Exhibition Park in Canberra on Saturday 18 July 2015.
The inaugural event promises to deliver a boutique indoor event for you and your dog featuring unique dining experiences, entertainment, information sessions, pampering and retail therapy for you and your dog.
The event aims to showcase activities and services available to the Canberra and regional dog community connecting the public with service providers most relevant to them. The varied programming means there is something on offer for dogs of all shapes and sizes.
The event also provides opportunity to indulge in an elegant High Tea experience with a bespoke menu tailored for you and your pooch.
Don’t miss out on being a part of this exciting new concept.
Source:- ACT Government
